<%@ page language="java" contentType="text/html; charset=UTF-8"
	pageEncoding="UTF-8"%>
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>About Us</title>
<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css"
	href="${pageContext.request.contextPath}/css/main/aboutAndContact.css" />
</head>
<body>


	<jsp:include page="header.jsp" />

	<main>
		<section class="hero">
			<h1>About Us</h1>
		</section>

		<section class="company-intro">
			<div class="intro-content">
				<div class="established">
					<h2>Established in 2022</h2>
				</div>
				<div class="intro-text">
					<p class="highlight-text">In the heart of Nepal, Kathmandu,
						stands Sanskritik Ghar, a symbol of innovation and cultural
						richness in hospitality and digital services.</p>

					<p>Driven by a passion for creativity and a dedication to
						excellence, the team at Sanskritik Ghar is committed to providing
						exceptional experiences for every guest. With a focus on building
						meaningful relationships, we ensure that every interaction is
						guided by trust, respect, and transparency. Together, we are not
						just offering hospitality; we are creating memorable moments that
						stand the test of time</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="quote-section">
			<div class="quote">
				<p>"Sanskritik Ghar: Where tradition meets modern hospitality,
					creating timeless experiences."</p>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="city-image">
			<img
				src="${pageContext.request.contextPath}/resources/founder/newbaneshwor.jpg"
				alt="New Baneshwor" class="newbaneshwor-img">
		</section>

		<section class="mission-vision-values">
			<div class="mission-section">
				<h2>Mission</h2>
				<p>At Sanskritik Ghar, our mission is to offer a welcoming place
					where guests can enjoy both traditional culture and modern comfort.
					We aim to provide excellent service and create unforgettable
					experiences that highlight the beauty of our heritage. Our goal is
					to make every guest feel at home while celebrating our cultural
					values.</p>
			</div>

			<div class="vision-section">
				<h2>Vision</h2>
				<p>Our vision at Sanskritik Ghar is to become a leading
					destination that blends cultural richness with exceptional
					hospitality. We strive to be a place where guests experience the
					warmth of tradition and the convenience of modern amenities. Our
					aim is to continuously improve and create a unique, memorable
					experience for every visitor.</p>
			</div>

			<div class="values-section">
				<h2>Values</h2>
				<p>At Sanskritik Ghar, we value integrity, respect, and
					excellence in everything we do. We are committed to providing a
					welcoming environment that celebrates cultural heritage while
					ensuring comfort and quality. Our focus is on customer
					satisfaction, continuous improvement, and sustainability. We
					believe in building lasting relationships with our guests and the
					community.</p>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="why-choose">
			<h2>Why Choose Sanskritik Ghar?</h2>
			<p>At Sanskritik Ghar, we offer a unique space that blends
				tradition and innovation, bringing together culture, creativity, and
				technology.</p>
			<p>We work closely with you to ensure that every aspect of our
				services aligns with your vision and values.</p>
			<p>Whether you’re a budding entrepreneur or an established
				business, Sanskritik Ghar helps elevate your brand and presence with
				deep expertise and a strong focus on authenticity. Let's collaborate
				to make your cultural or creative vision a reality.</p>
		</section>

		<section class="greeting-section">
			<h2>Greetings! from our team</h2>
		</section>



		<section class="founder">
			<div class="founder-image">
				<img
					src="${pageContext.request.contextPath}/resources/founder/hari.png"
					alt="Hari" class="founder-img">
			</div>
			<div class="founder-bio">
				<h3>Hari Chandra Adhikari</h3>

				<p>Greetings! I’m the founder of Sanskritik Ghar, a cultural
					hospitality space based in Kathmandu. Since our beginning, we've
					been committed to offering an authentic blend of tradition and
					comfort to every guest. From cozy stays to warm service, our team
					ensures a memorable experience rooted in Nepali culture. If you
					have any questions or want to connect, we’re always here for you.
					We look forward to welcoming you soon!</p>

				<p>
					Warm regards,<br>Hari Chandra Adhikari<br> Founder, Sanskritik
					Ghar
				</p>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="founder">
			<div class="founder-image">
				<img
					src="${pageContext.request.contextPath}/resources/founder/nischal.png"
					alt="Nischal" class="founder-img">
			</div>
			<div class="founder-bio">
				<h3>Nischal Tharu Lohabaria</h3>

				<p>Namaste! As the co-founder of Sanskritik Ghar, it brings me
					great joy to be part of a space that celebrates Nepali culture and
					heartfelt hospitality. Our goal is to create more than just a stay
					— we aim to give you a true cultural experience, filled with
					warmth, tradition, and care. Thank you for choosing us, and we look
					forward to welcoming you like family.</p>

				<p>
					Warm regards,<br>Nischal Tharu Lohabaria<br> Co-Founder,
					Sanskritik Ghar
				</p>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="founder">
			<div class="founder-image">
				<img
					src="${pageContext.request.contextPath}/resources/founder/injamamul.png"
					alt="Injamam" class="founder-img">
			</div>
			<div class="founder-bio">
				<h3>Md Injamamul Haque</h3>

				<p>Namaste and welcome to Sanskritik Ghar. As the Managing
					Director, my focus is on ensuring every guest experiences the
					warmth, culture, and hospitality that defines our space. We are
					committed to creating a place where tradition meets comfort. Thank
					you for trusting us — we’re excited to have you with us.</p>

				<p>
					Warm regards,<br>Md Injamamul Haque<br> Managing Director,
					Sanskritik Ghar
				</p>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="founder">
			<div class="founder-image">
				<img
					src="${pageContext.request.contextPath}/resources/founder/abhinav.png"
					alt="Abhinav" class="founder-img">
			</div>
			<div class="founder-bio">
				<h3>Abhinav Shah</h3>

				<p>Namaste! I’m honored to welcome you to Sanskritik Ghar, where
					every dish tells a story. As the Head Chef, my passion lies in
					blending authentic Nepali flavors with modern twists to create a
					memorable dining experience. We cook with heart, culture, and love
					— and I can’t wait for you to taste it.</p>
				<p>
					Warm regards,<br>Abhinav Shah<br> Head Chef,
					Sanskritik Ghar
				</p>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="founder">
			<div class="founder-image">
				<img
					src="${pageContext.request.contextPath}/resources/founder/binod.jpg"
					alt="Binod" class="founder-img">
			</div>
			<div class="founder-bio">
				<h3>Binod Sarki</h3>

				<p>Namaste! As the Head Manager of Sanskritik Ghar, I’m
					committed to ensuring every guest enjoys a smooth, warm, and
					memorable experience. From your first step in to your last goodbye,
					our team is here to serve you with genuine hospitality and care. We
					look forward to welcoming you soon!</p>
				<p>
					Warm regards,<br>Binod Sarki<br> Head Manager, Sanskritik
					Ghar
				</p>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="join-team">
			<h2>Join Our Team</h2>
			<p>There are currently no open positions at Sanskritik Ghar.
				Please check again in the near future.</p>
		</section>
	</main>


</body>
</html>